# Repository-specific DOC_SYNC rule extensions preserved across upgrade.
# Base file: .orch/rules/app/docsync.rules
app/internal/config,deploy/.env.runtime.example,deploy/.env.dev.example|docs/app/config.md,deploy/.env.runtime.example,deploy/.env.dev.example|config changes must update config docs and env examples
app/internal/transport/httpapi,app/openapi|docs/app/api.md,app/openapi/openapi.yaml|api changes must update docs and contract
app/internal/service/example,app/internal/infra/store/postgres,app/db/migrations|docs/app/architecture.md|domain and storage changes must update architecture docs
app/internal/service/shared,app/internal/transport/httpapi/httpx,app/internal/transport/httpapi/middleware|docs/app/errors.md|error code baseline changes must update docs/app/errors.md
